{"tid":1253933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"訴求升級 重提真普選","createTime":"2019-06-24T00:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T15:27:50.000Z","uid":52609,"like":56,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4237485e381498672e12f7708b915bc1466d3b","tid":1253933,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:07:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190624&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20711950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190624%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20711950&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr16b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=efe45a93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190624%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20711950&h=d7a6642c\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190624&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20711950</a><br />\n<br />\n美國跨黨派國會議員本月重推的《香港人權和民主法案》，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>當中設下2020年普選立法會的「時限」，並明確要求普選特首</strong></span></span>，法案如獲通過，港府若不作回應，勢影響《香港政策法》，最嚴重可換來美方制裁，變相迫令港府重啟政改。<br />\n<br />\nThis way sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫緩送中、5人暴動、致歉、暫緩國歌法、暫緩明日大嶼......<br />\n<br />\n以上全部都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨緩兵之計，拖字訣</span></strong></span>，希望首先冷卻事情，G20後再處理，拖到我地無方向、內部路線分歧，鬼打鬼，民情消散，再硬推、秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n如果繼續只談五大訴求，會失去部分民意支持。<br />\n因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">部分人會覺得政府好似已經聽左民意</span></strong></span>，又暫緩、又道歉。但係我地仲繼續升級行動，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地係無理取罵，係搞事</span></span></strong>。繼續落去，我地民意基礎只會不斷減弱，最後被逐一擊破。<br />\n<br />\n所以要將<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">訴求升級</span></span></strong>，因為政府只聽黨意，並非民意，若不進行真普選，送中會重來、廿三條會重來、國歌法會重來。同時在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">G20前對中共施以最大壓力，提供子彈比Trump出聲幫香港</span></span></strong>，亦令<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動升級出師有名</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 爭取真普選，將「公民提名」及「政黨提名」納入行政長官選舉提名程序<br />\n2. 立法會廢除功能組別<br />\n3. 全國人大常委撤回政改決議<br />\n4. 重新啟動政改諮詢"},{"pid":"00fb2deaef1c0ca6d75783c4fef643e2636225e9","tid":1253933,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"472c5cbf2361d9ec946d0a3f7de5426f1e73f440","tid":1253933,"uid":97212,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"開始少人氣 仲加野？"},{"pid":"85609b9e2c31691716ab515359f679a36cf51ebe","tid":1253933,"uid":72063,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:19:07.000Z","msg":"你傻的嗎？"},{"pid":"5ddb667712120dfe027a305676554c254bc0d46a","tid":1253933,"uid":240352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:21:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e1015254587304883d991906a51aaac22c1c4bd","tid":1253933,"uid":129436,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:38:49.000Z","msg":"個問題係個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d288b2694ea9faf4a2beb033dacf83c19cddb73","tid":1253933,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:48:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0769e6cce00896f9641741d38a9941f9febcbcef","tid":1253933,"uid":28279,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原本四大都未成功仲要加料"},{"pid":"b7845a06b09ab5fdc9c79095c9a8c2edeec88ded","tid":1253933,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d92ed47480c92556728b3297c04c174ab3589299","tid":1253933,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset